		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Go the eBay route.  I tried all sorts of alternatives to an actual FDS belt and even though they'd functionally work, the drive itself would always get I/O errors or experience other oddities often the result of a misaligned belt.
<br />
<br />I ended up just buying a belt off eBay (at the time going for around US$20 + S/H from Japan); problem solved.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


